src/parallel/ll-dgr-src/prestream_g.f File Reference

Detailed Description

Pre-Stream and Strean steps for pressure distribution function g in the parallel dual grid D2Q9 Lee-Lin multiphase LBM.

The pre-stream step is done in g, which is then streamed into gbar.

Directional differentials are evaluated using a second order switching differential scheme (biased/central). Other differentials are evaluated using a standard second order central differencing scheme.
